00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:47,759
Boss.

2
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:49,240
Please come in.

3
00:01:53,759 --> 00:01:54,360
Mrs. Wang.

4
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,680
I came here today

5
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:58,280
to tell you a story.

6
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:05,160
This is what Cao Tai placed in the shrine.

7
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:07,690
It is also Jiang Siyan's relic.

8
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:13,600
Cao Tai was afraid of seeing ghosts,

9
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,800
perhaps because he killed Jiang Siyan.

10
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:18,200
But I never understood.

11
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:22,520
Cao Tai had no grudge against the Jiang family,

12
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:24,120
why did he kill Jiang Siyan?

13
00:02:25,079 --> 00:02:26,840
Until Wang Wan told me

14
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:30,040
that this handkerchief was hers.

15
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:32,240
It was raining heavily that day.

16
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,770
She handed me the umbrella,

17
00:02:34,200 --> 00:02:36,640
so I took off my cloak and put it on her.

18
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:39,000
On a rainy night eight years ago,

19
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:41,440
Jiang Siyan was wearing Wang Wan's clothes,

20
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:43,370
and both were girls of the same age.

21
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:45,480
In the blurred vision of the rainy night,

22
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:48,160
Cao Tai mistook Jiang Siyan for Wang Wan.

23
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:01,650
Cao Tai wanted to kill Wang Wan,

24
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,770
and it could only be because of you.

25
00:03:04,160 --> 00:03:06,560
Cao Tai used to get medicine from you often.

26
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:07,840
Over time,

27
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:11,440
taking advantage of your husband and Wang Wan being out at the same time,

28
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:12,640
you two got together.

29
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:15,680
After you accidentally miscarried,

30
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,940
you believed it was Wang Wan harming you.

31
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:22,579
You intended to kill Wang Wan.

32
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:25,360
You tricked Cao Tai into believing the child was his,

33
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:27,440
wanting to take advantage of Dr. Wang going out to gather herbs

34
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:29,640
to have Cao Tai kill Wang Wan.

35
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,500
Old Wang went to gather herbs.

36
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:44,960
Wang Wan walks past here every day.

37
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:48,360
Tonight is the best time to strike.

38
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,079
If you are a man,

39
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,880
prove it to me.

40
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,450
Wait for my news.

41
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:01,020
The rain was too heavy,

42
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,890
I couldn't see clearly.

43
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,200
And I was very nervous at the time,

44
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:07,000
I didn't even dare to look at her.

45
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:10,160
It wasn't until I strangled her to death

46
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:13,370
that I realized I killed the wrong person.

47
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,010
What should I do?

48
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,400
What should I do?

49
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:20,660
You can't even kill the right person.

50
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:25,130
I can't sleep well every night now,

51
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:29,420
dreaming every night that she comes to question me.

52
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:31,400
We had no grudges against each other,

53
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:32,560
why did I kill her?

54
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:38,120
I want to surrender to the authorities.

55
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:41,680
I am going to surrender to the authorities.

56
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,360
Surrender?

57
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,400
What will you tell the authorities?

58
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:49,000
Why did you kill that girl?

59
00:06:49,960 --> 00:06:51,640
Don't drag me into this.

60
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,040
You can't even kill the right person,

61
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,640
what else can you do?

62
00:06:58,120 --> 00:07:00,520
I am going to surrender to the authorities.

63
00:07:02,600 --> 00:07:03,720
You idiot!

64
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,000
Listen to me.

65
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:30,840
Find a grave

66
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:33,900
and hide her in someone else's grave.

67
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:36,640
Pretend this never happened,

68
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,760
understand?

69
00:07:49,159 --> 00:07:49,820
What a pity.

70
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,920
Cao Tai ultimately chose not to surrender.

71
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,000
Feeling guilty,

72
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:56,800
he put Jiang Siyan's handkerchief in the shrine,

73
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:58,320
burning incense every day,

74
00:07:58,320 --> 00:08:01,600
praying for Jiang Siyan to have good fortune in her next life.

75
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,600
The Jiang family lost their youngest daughter,

76
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:06,840
so they treated the foundling Wanqing as Jiang Siyan,

77
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,200
raising her for eight years.

78
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:16,130
Cao Tai hasn't had a good night's sleep in these eight years.

79
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,800
You also know that

80
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:24,100
seeing a ghost was the last straw that broke Cao Tai.

81
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:32,210
You know even better

82
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:33,840
that if things continued like this,

83
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:36,039
Cao Tai would definitely turn himself in.

84
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:37,679
So you played the ghost

85
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:40,260
to lure Cao Tai into committing suicide.

86
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:54,960
I am Jiang Siyan.

87
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,880
Aren't you a child?

88
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:01,440
I've grown up.

89
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:05,240
I am not happy down there at all.

90
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,440
I'm sorry.

91
00:09:07,160 --> 00:09:07,880
I'm really sorry.

92
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:09,040
I was wrong.

93
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:12,800
Don't you feel guilty?

94
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:15,240
Come down and keep me company.

95
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:16,600
That way,

96
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:19,080
you won't owe me anymore.

97
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:52,130
You must have boiled a lot of cough powder yesterday.

98
00:09:52,840 --> 00:09:56,760
It contains schizonepeta, balloon flower, aster,

99
00:09:57,160 --> 00:10:00,120
stemona, licorice, and dried tangerine peel.

100
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:04,080
Among them, the smell of schizonepeta is the strongest.

101
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:06,880
Even if you bathed and applied rouge and powder,

102
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:10,120
I can still smell it.

103
00:10:13,640 --> 00:10:14,760
Are you saying

104
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:18,000
that I instigated Cao Tai to hang himself?

105
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,560
This is all your deduction.

106
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:22,020
What evidence do you have?

107
00:10:22,240 --> 00:10:23,520
You want evidence?

108
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:30,120
I happen to have evidence.

109
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:34,280
This is Zhou's shoe shop's ledger from yesterday.

110
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:36,400
The shop assistant clearly told me

111
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:40,130
that you went to buy embroidered shoes with an umbrella yesterday.

112
00:10:40,760 --> 00:10:42,520
Didn't you tell us yesterday

113
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:44,940
that you didn't go out after the rain?

114
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:47,620
Why did you buy those embroidered shoes?

115
00:10:54,280 --> 00:10:56,080
Actually, I've been wondering,

116
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:58,330
if you cover half your face,

117
00:10:58,880 --> 00:11:00,120
how do you make Cao Tai

118
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:02,880
believe that you are the grown-up Jiang Siyan?

119
00:11:03,760 --> 00:11:05,090
It can only be the shoes.

120
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:06,760
You definitely bought a pair

121
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:09,320
of embroidered shoes exactly like Jiang Siyan's.

122
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,120
Am I right?

123
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:26,920
Cao Tai.

124
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:30,320
You dragged me down even in death.

125
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:33,400
So,

126
00:11:34,280 --> 00:11:36,010
you want to confess right here?

127
00:11:37,720 --> 00:11:39,040
But I must remind you,

128
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:41,240
if you falsely confess

129
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:43,680
and affect the investigation of the case,

130
00:11:43,680 --> 00:11:47,210
according to the Tang Code, the punishment will be more severe.

131
00:12:00,280 --> 00:12:01,940
According to your deduction,

132
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:04,180
he really killed someone.

133
00:12:04,920 --> 00:12:08,440
I thought he never did it.

134
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:13,580
Where is the mound?

135
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:15,810
There was clearly a mound here.

136
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:21,000
I followed your instructions

137
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,730
and buried the wrong body here.

138
00:12:23,640 --> 00:12:25,500
If you really killed Jiang Siyan,

139
00:12:25,880 --> 00:12:28,160
why would Old Jiang report it to the authorities?

140
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:30,290
I heard a constable say with my own ears

141
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:33,580
that Old Jiang's daughter disappeared just a few days ago.

142
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:36,290
Open your eyes and look!

143
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,660
Look for yourself!

144
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,970
Old Jiang's only daughter.

145
00:12:44,400 --> 00:12:45,840
Then who did I kill?

146
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:47,770
Eight years ago,

147
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,800
you didn't kill anyone at all.

148
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:53,000
You were just afraid I'd call you a coward,

149
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:55,360
so you came back and lied to me that you killed the wrong person.

150
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:57,960
I can't believe I trusted you for so many years!

151
00:12:59,880 --> 00:13:00,880
No, it's impossible.

152
00:13:00,880 --> 00:13:01,640
Believe me,

153
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:04,120
I really killed her.

154
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:05,770
Where are the bones?

155
00:13:06,160 --> 00:13:08,040
Didn't you say you buried them in someone else's mound?

156
00:13:08,040 --> 00:13:09,100
Where is the mound?

157
00:13:12,960 --> 00:13:13,880
Let go!

158
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:16,840
Listen to me. Listen to me. Listen to me.

159
00:13:17,920 --> 00:13:20,120
I really killed her and buried her here.

160
00:13:21,880 --> 00:13:23,280
Could it be that she turned into a ghost

161
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,480
and came back to life?

162
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,760
So the body disappeared?

163
00:13:27,920 --> 00:13:28,780
Get out of here!

164
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:30,280
You loser!

165
00:13:30,760 --> 00:13:31,720
Loser!

166
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:33,200
I killed her

167
00:13:33,800 --> 00:13:35,260
and buried her right here.

168
00:13:40,160 --> 00:13:40,800
She must be

169
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:42,840
right

170
00:13:43,280 --> 00:13:45,120
here!

171
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:46,240
I killed her.

172
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:47,920
It must be here.

173
00:13:48,640 --> 00:13:49,520
It must be here.

174
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,690
What are you doing here?

175
00:14:07,160 --> 00:14:09,360
Let's go report to the officials, okay?

176
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:18,560
I used to comfort you

177
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:19,560
because you killed someone,

178
00:14:19,560 --> 00:14:20,920
and I was afraid you'd drag me down.

179
00:14:20,920 --> 00:14:22,320
Now that you haven't,

180
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,420
what am I afraid of?

181
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,360
Go report it.

182
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:27,050
If you don't believe me,

183
00:14:27,920 --> 00:14:29,760
I'll tell Dr. Wang

184
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:31,560
about our affair!

185
00:14:53,040 --> 00:14:54,040
I believe you.

186
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:55,720
I believe you.

187
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:58,160
It's been so many years,

188
00:14:58,400 --> 00:15:01,440
maybe you just forgot the place.

189
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:06,560
Go back first.

190
00:15:07,080 --> 00:15:08,280
We'll figure this out

191
00:15:08,560 --> 00:15:10,360
later.

192
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:18,960
After he left,

193
00:15:20,040 --> 00:15:21,640
I wanted to kill him.

194
00:15:22,520 --> 00:15:24,120
Since he's afraid of ghosts,

195
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:26,480
I'll pretend to be one.

196
00:15:28,880 --> 00:15:30,800
Since you say he killed someone,

197
00:15:31,200 --> 00:15:32,330
where are the bones?

198
00:15:32,560 --> 00:15:34,160
There are no bones.

199
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:42,360
A few days ago, a family was moving a grave

200
00:15:42,680 --> 00:15:44,740
and happened to dig up two skeletons.

201
00:15:44,880 --> 00:15:46,800
One of them was Jiang Siyan's.

202
00:15:47,560 --> 00:15:48,640
By mistake,

203
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:50,760
how could you find her bones?

204
00:15:53,040 --> 00:15:54,040
In my opinion,

205
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:58,360
those who pretend to be evil will eventually be haunted by it.

206
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:17,960
It's time for a shift change, right?

207
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:18,600
Yeah,

208
00:16:18,640 --> 00:16:19,320
let's go.

209
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:22,330
There must be the information I want here.

210
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:41,320
The archives hold all the files of the government office,

211
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:42,640
it's an important place.

212
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:44,520
Irrelevant people can't enter.

213
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:47,480
Keep a close eye on this place.

214
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:48,040
Yes.

215
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,890
It's done, Sister. Su Lang,

216
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:55,360
I've sorted out Jiang Siyan's belongings,

217
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:56,680
go give them to Uncle Jiang.

218
00:16:56,680 --> 00:16:57,560
Okay.

219
00:16:58,520 --> 00:17:00,560
Constable Su, I beg you,

220
00:17:00,640 --> 00:17:02,160
please help me.

221
00:17:02,640 --> 00:17:04,400
I have no other choice!

222
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:06,160
Alright, what's the use of begging me?

223
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:07,680
We're just constables,

224
00:17:07,960 --> 00:17:09,089
I can't judge cases.

225
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:10,680
How the lord will judge tomorrow,

226
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:11,359
is up to him.

227
00:17:14,599 --> 00:17:15,560
Officers,

228
00:17:16,359 --> 00:17:18,359
Officers, I beg you.

229
00:17:18,880 --> 00:17:21,240
My wife is about to die,

230
00:17:21,520 --> 00:17:24,839
she just wants to see her daughter before she dies.

231
00:17:26,319 --> 00:17:30,000
Please be lenient, officers,

232
00:17:30,520 --> 00:17:34,320
let my wife fulfill this wish before she dies.

233
00:17:34,520 --> 00:17:35,800
I beg you!

234
00:17:35,840 --> 00:17:36,880
Get up first,

235
00:17:37,200 --> 00:17:38,200
stand up and talk.

236
00:17:41,320 --> 00:17:42,120
Uncle Jiang,

237
00:17:43,280 --> 00:17:44,410
the law has no mercy.

238
00:17:45,120 --> 00:17:48,200
And she is already waiting for the Ministry of Justice's sentence.

239
00:17:48,200 --> 00:17:50,330
She is not your daughter, Jiang Siyan.

240
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:53,520
I know.

241
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:56,200
In these eight years,

242
00:17:57,360 --> 00:18:01,200
we have long regarded her as our biological daughter.

243
00:18:01,640 --> 00:18:03,040
I pinned all my love

244
00:18:03,240 --> 00:18:05,960
on her.

245
00:18:07,760 --> 00:18:09,880
The Wanqing you speak of

246
00:18:10,960 --> 00:18:13,240
is my daughter.

247
00:18:19,760 --> 00:18:20,440
Catcher Su.

248
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:23,240
Bring Wanqing out tomorrow.

249
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:25,880
We need to identify the crime scene.

250
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:40,000
Daughter,

251
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:42,680
Siyan,

252
00:18:44,600 --> 00:18:46,400
Dad is here to see you.

253
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:49,280
My child.

254
00:18:55,240 --> 00:18:56,040
Daughter.

255
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:26,800
Siyan.

256
00:19:38,120 --> 00:19:38,840
Siyan.

257
00:19:40,240 --> 00:19:42,040
Am I dreaming?

258
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:46,080
You are really my Siyan.

259
00:19:47,280 --> 00:19:50,080
You are finally back.

260
00:19:52,840 --> 00:19:54,100
Your daughter is back.

261
00:19:54,240 --> 00:19:56,000
My child,

262
00:19:59,760 --> 00:20:01,880
you are finally back.

263
00:20:02,920 --> 00:20:04,800
Come, let me look at you.

264
00:20:07,160 --> 00:20:09,640
Did you eat well out there?

265
00:20:10,240 --> 00:20:11,720
Did anyone bully you?

266
00:20:11,760 --> 00:20:13,640
N-no one bullied me.

267
00:20:13,800 --> 00:20:14,840
Mom, don't worry.

268
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:16,200
I'm fine. Stop it.

269
00:20:17,920 --> 00:20:19,960
My child.

270
00:20:20,960 --> 00:20:22,000
Let me tell you.

271
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:23,200
Looking at it now,

272
00:20:23,560 --> 00:20:25,620
Nanrong Xiang is the most miserable.

273
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:28,000
When I went to inform him of the case,

274
00:20:28,520 --> 00:20:29,560
as soon as he heard

275
00:20:29,640 --> 00:20:32,920
that Wanqing and Wanrou were both locked up,

276
00:20:33,040 --> 00:20:34,480
he went crazy.

277
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:36,960
The dancers of the Jiaofang have been dismissed.

278
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:39,120
Now, he sits at the door every day,

279
00:20:39,160 --> 00:20:41,640
drinking and singing to passers-by.

280
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:43,380
Nanrong Xiang and Ye Xian.

281
00:20:43,680 --> 00:20:45,600
If he could have treated them equally

282
00:20:45,600 --> 00:20:47,280
and taken good care of both sisters back then,

283
00:20:47,280 --> 00:20:49,140
wouldn't this have been avoided?

284
00:20:49,440 --> 00:20:51,040
After Wanqing was locked up,

285
00:20:51,280 --> 00:20:52,800
she didn't even see her biological father,

286
00:20:52,800 --> 00:20:56,330
yet she has such deep affection for Mother Jiang who raised her.

287
00:20:58,200 --> 00:21:01,200
Relatives are often assumed to be connected by blood,

288
00:21:02,040 --> 00:21:04,200
but deep companionship is the key.

289
00:21:05,520 --> 00:21:06,360
For example.

290
00:21:07,320 --> 00:21:09,760
Suppose you were accidentally switched when you were young

291
00:21:09,760 --> 00:21:12,360
and lived in a family with no blood relation.

292
00:21:13,440 --> 00:21:15,480
At this time, your biological father appears.

293
00:21:15,480 --> 00:21:16,440
If it were you,

294
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:18,200
how would you choose?

295
00:21:19,080 --> 00:21:21,680
Of course, I'd choose the father who raised me.

296
00:21:22,400 --> 00:21:23,080
Catcher Su.

297
00:21:23,600 --> 00:21:25,130
Am I your biological child?

298
00:21:26,600 --> 00:21:27,640
You brat.

299
00:21:28,360 --> 00:21:30,320
I picked you up in the garbage dump.

300
00:21:30,960 --> 00:21:32,160
Picked me up?

301
00:21:32,480 --> 00:21:33,320
Then tell me,

302
00:21:33,480 --> 00:21:35,940
what was the situation when you picked me up?

303
00:21:36,480 --> 00:21:39,540
What else was in the garbage dump? Don't go, wait for me.

304
00:21:39,840 --> 00:21:40,970
Where are you going?

305
00:21:41,560 --> 00:21:42,240
Wait for me.

306
00:21:42,800 --> 00:21:44,330
Why are you walking so fast?

307
00:21:44,840 --> 00:21:46,720
Now, deducting two taels,

308
00:21:46,800 --> 00:21:48,400
you still owe me eight taels.

309
00:21:49,080 --> 00:21:50,280
You are quite honest.

310
00:21:50,640 --> 00:21:51,560
Of course.

311
00:21:51,760 --> 00:21:54,920
I, Li Jinglan, never owe anyone a single cent.

312
00:21:57,360 --> 00:21:58,200
In that case.

313
00:21:59,680 --> 00:22:01,520
I want to help you investigate cases in the future.

314
00:22:01,520 --> 00:22:03,320
Why don't you give me an identity

315
00:22:03,520 --> 00:22:04,980
and let me be a Buliangren?

316
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:09,400
That way, when I go out in the future, my status will be perfectly justifiable.

317
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:12,330
You want to go to the archives to check the case files.

318
00:22:14,520 --> 00:22:15,560
Actually,

319
00:22:16,760 --> 00:22:19,290
I looked into your mother's autopsy records.

320
00:22:20,520 --> 00:22:22,980
She had multiple struggle marks on her body.

321
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:26,080
Both her wrists and ankles were broken.

322
00:22:26,800 --> 00:22:31,460
A sharp knife with a blue dragon and roaring tiger pattern was found next to the body.

323
00:22:33,080 --> 00:22:34,680
She was a medical woman at the medicine shop.

324
00:22:34,680 --> 00:22:36,440
I really don't know who

325
00:22:36,480 --> 00:22:38,810
would have such a deep grudge against her.

326
00:22:39,880 --> 00:22:41,760
You can't bear to see corpses.

327
00:22:42,800 --> 00:22:44,260
That should be the reason.

328
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:47,660
This is my private matter.

329
00:22:49,480 --> 00:22:51,280
If you really want to be a Bad Man,

330
00:22:51,520 --> 00:22:52,520
I can help you.

331
00:22:53,680 --> 00:22:54,680
Magistrate Chen.

332
00:23:01,480 --> 00:23:02,880
Magistrate Chen.

333
00:23:06,320 --> 00:23:08,400
Magistrate Chen.

334
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:32,200
Miss Li.

335
00:23:32,240 --> 00:23:33,360
Why are you here?

336
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:36,200
You've solved several cases in a row.

337
00:23:36,320 --> 00:23:38,380
You're the favorite in the yamen now.

338
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:39,640
You flatter me.

339
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:41,840
It's all thanks to Magistrate Chen's good guidance.

340
00:23:41,840 --> 00:23:44,880
I strongly support you being a coroner.

341
00:23:44,960 --> 00:23:46,720
As for your bet with Vice Magistrate Li,

342
00:23:46,720 --> 00:23:48,000
I also bet you'll win.

343
00:23:48,520 --> 00:23:50,580
Magistrate Chen, you have a good eye.

344
00:23:52,120 --> 00:23:54,240
What are you doing?

345
00:23:57,640 --> 00:23:58,440
Nothing.

346
00:23:58,720 --> 00:24:03,080
I just came specifically to bring you some dry brewed wine.

347
00:24:04,240 --> 00:24:05,480
I can't take this.

348
00:24:05,560 --> 00:24:07,240
Last time, because I drank your wine,

349
00:24:07,240 --> 00:24:09,600
I got drunk and allowed you to be a coroner.

350
00:24:09,640 --> 00:24:12,320
As a result, Vice Magistrate Li scolded me for three days straight.

351
00:24:12,320 --> 00:24:13,160
I won't fall for it this time.

352
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:14,280
Yes, you can.

353
00:24:14,760 --> 00:24:15,320
No, no.

354
00:24:15,360 --> 00:24:16,080
Yes, you can.

355
00:24:16,080 --> 00:24:16,960
No, take it away.

356
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:17,880
You can.

357
00:24:18,240 --> 00:24:19,240
No.

358
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:21,760
This time it's not for me.

359
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:26,720
Not for you?

360
00:24:27,600 --> 00:24:30,360
Who else could make you worry so much?

361
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:33,360
Jueming.

362
00:24:34,800 --> 00:24:35,560
Jueming?

363
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:40,360
The assistant who helped me with the case, Jueming.

364
00:24:42,720 --> 00:24:45,160
This person is extraordinarily capable.

365
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:47,840
He is definitely the talent our yamen needs.

366
00:24:48,320 --> 00:24:49,320
You want him

367
00:24:49,680 --> 00:24:51,240
to be a Bad Man?

368
00:24:52,720 --> 00:24:53,360
No, no.

369
00:24:53,400 --> 00:24:55,280
The list of Bad Men has long been set.

370
00:24:55,280 --> 00:24:56,600
No, no.

371
00:24:57,880 --> 00:24:59,240
Father, you're here.

372
00:25:00,920 --> 00:25:01,440
Miss Li.

373
00:25:04,280 --> 00:25:06,540
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven.

374
00:25:08,960 --> 00:25:10,440
No, Miss Li.

375
00:25:23,360 --> 00:25:24,280
Miss Li insists

376
00:25:24,320 --> 00:25:25,960
that I test your martial arts.

377
00:25:25,960 --> 00:25:28,080
Let's see if you can pass the Bad Man test.

378
00:25:28,080 --> 00:25:30,080
Then don't blame me for being rough.

379
00:26:08,200 --> 00:26:09,120
First round.

380
00:26:09,240 --> 00:26:10,400
Jueming wins.

381
00:26:11,080 --> 00:26:12,200
Good, beautiful!

382
00:26:17,240 --> 00:26:18,320
Liu Zhuang wins.

383
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:30,720
Second round, Xiao Yi wins.

384
00:26:33,800 --> 00:26:34,920
Final round.

385
00:26:54,800 --> 00:26:56,200
It's because I taught him well.

386
00:26:56,200 --> 00:26:57,280
I am his master.

387
00:26:57,360 --> 00:26:58,960
You taught him well.

388
00:27:42,720 --> 00:27:44,120
Jueming wins.

389
00:27:50,680 --> 00:27:51,840
From today on,

390
00:27:52,280 --> 00:27:54,160
you are a Bad Man.

391
00:27:54,600 --> 00:27:55,720
Follow Constable Su

392
00:27:55,720 --> 00:27:57,650
and wait for his orders at any time.

393
00:27:57,720 --> 00:27:59,120
As for your new home,

394
00:28:00,040 --> 00:28:00,920
Don't worry.

395
00:28:01,280 --> 00:28:03,480
We'll help you clean up.

396
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:04,680
We.

397
00:28:06,840 --> 00:28:08,320
Guys, clean it up properly.

398
00:28:08,320 --> 00:28:09,600
Clean that side up too.

399
00:28:11,160 --> 00:28:13,090
Hey, wipe that window frame again.

400
00:28:13,560 --> 00:28:15,200
Throw away that broken flower pot in the corner.

401
00:28:15,200 --> 00:28:16,600
You guys are so careless.

402
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:17,880
Gently.

403
00:28:18,840 --> 00:28:20,570
Put this table in the wing room.

404
00:28:21,280 --> 00:28:21,960
Be careful.

405
00:28:22,000 --> 00:28:23,440
This table is very expensive.

406
00:28:23,440 --> 00:28:24,640
Move it to the parlor.

407
00:28:25,520 --> 00:28:26,280
From now on,

408
00:28:26,600 --> 00:28:28,600
you stick close to me,

409
00:28:28,680 --> 00:28:30,120
and we'll roam the martial world together.

410
00:28:30,120 --> 00:28:31,320
We'll share our wine,

411
00:28:31,320 --> 00:28:32,560
and solve cases together.

412
00:28:32,560 --> 00:28:34,820
You're not allowed to sneak off halfway.

413
00:28:53,360 --> 00:28:54,120
Honglian.

414
00:28:55,240 --> 00:28:55,920
Honglian.

415
00:29:01,240 --> 00:29:02,280
When the red flower is outside,

416
00:29:02,280 --> 00:29:03,480
my father isn't home.

417
00:29:04,040 --> 00:29:06,500
I brought you some delicious food. Let's go.

418
00:29:12,840 --> 00:29:15,040
Here, try it. It's still hot.

419
00:29:16,880 --> 00:29:18,080
Watch your sleeves.

420
00:29:22,480 --> 00:29:23,540
Your father again.

421
00:29:35,760 --> 00:29:36,480
So sweet.

422
00:29:41,320 --> 00:29:41,760
If your father...

423
00:29:41,760 --> 00:29:43,640
Zhen'er probably hasn't had this.

424
00:29:43,640 --> 00:29:45,640
Let's bring some to her to try.

425
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:48,020
Who is Zhen'er?

426
00:29:49,160 --> 00:29:50,480
Sister Qiuhua's youngest daughter.

427
00:29:50,480 --> 00:29:52,410
She's very well-behaved and cute.

428
00:29:54,960 --> 00:29:57,440
If you had told me earlier, I would have brought an extra portion.

429
00:29:57,440 --> 00:29:58,400
It's fine.

430
00:29:58,680 --> 00:30:00,360
I can't finish a whole bowl anyway.

431
00:30:00,360 --> 00:30:02,020
Let's go and bring some to her.

432
00:30:02,720 --> 00:30:03,280
Okay.

433
00:30:06,920 --> 00:30:07,840
Is this the place?

434
00:30:07,840 --> 00:30:08,440
Yes.

435
00:30:09,760 --> 00:30:11,090
Sister Qiuhua's house.

436
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:12,740
Okay, let's go.

437
00:30:15,800 --> 00:30:16,480
Be careful.

438
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:20,800
She will definitely like the porridge we brought her.

439
00:30:20,800 --> 00:30:21,600
Open the door.

440
00:30:22,320 --> 00:30:23,400
Sister Qiuhua!

441
00:30:25,280 --> 00:30:26,540
Wait for me at the door.

442
00:30:38,680 --> 00:30:39,240
This...

443
00:30:40,240 --> 00:30:41,040
What's wrong?

444
00:30:42,320 --> 00:30:43,600
She died in bed.

445
00:30:44,040 --> 00:30:45,900
And her state of death is bizarre.

446
00:30:59,080 --> 00:31:03,040
The deceased's face and lips are cyanotic.

447
00:31:05,040 --> 00:31:07,040
Her eyes are bloodshot and swollen.

448
00:31:08,440 --> 00:31:10,040
Her nails are bluish-purple.

449
00:31:10,040 --> 00:31:13,200
Her hands, feet, and head

450
00:31:13,720 --> 00:31:16,120
were bound by red ropes and suspended.

451
00:31:18,320 --> 00:31:20,450
The ligature marks are quite obvious.

452
00:31:20,640 --> 00:31:22,840
The rope marks are evenly distributed.

453
00:31:22,840 --> 00:31:26,240
She died of asphyxiation by strangulation with the red rope.

454
00:31:31,800 --> 00:31:34,060
There's a large incantation on her back.

455
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:37,660
It looks like it was drawn with cinnabar.

456
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:40,460
Looking at her condition,

457
00:31:41,560 --> 00:31:44,040
she didn't struggle much before she died.

458
00:31:44,480 --> 00:31:46,320
But we can also rule out suicide by hanging.

459
00:31:46,320 --> 00:31:47,250
It's a homicide.

460
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:49,600
Livor mortis is quite pronounced.

461
00:31:49,600 --> 00:31:52,330
Time of death was around the hour of Xu last night.

462
00:31:59,640 --> 00:32:00,600
This stove

463
00:32:01,360 --> 00:32:03,560
has been used to brew Shenqi decoction.

464
00:32:03,960 --> 00:32:06,820
Someone in this house must have had kidney disease.

465
00:32:16,600 --> 00:32:18,130
Besides the smell of herbs,

466
00:32:19,480 --> 00:32:22,140
there's a strong scent of Chinese honey locust.

467
00:32:24,640 --> 00:32:27,440
The deceased's lips are slightly curved upwards.

468
00:32:27,840 --> 00:32:29,700
Why would she smile before dying?

469
00:32:29,800 --> 00:32:30,480
Honglian.

470
00:32:31,400 --> 00:32:32,330
Don't be too sad.

471
00:32:32,880 --> 00:32:34,560
We will definitely get to the bottom of this

472
00:32:34,560 --> 00:32:36,400
and get justice for Sister Qiuhua.

473
00:32:36,400 --> 00:32:37,200
Stop crying.

474
00:32:38,600 --> 00:32:39,930
When was the body found?

475
00:32:40,440 --> 00:32:41,680
During the hours of the Snake.

476
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:42,920
The deceased is Qiuhua.

477
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:44,400
She was a washerwoman around the dock.

478
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:46,400
She made a living washing clothes for boatmen

479
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:49,060
and had a six-year-old daughter named Zhen'er.

480
00:32:51,440 --> 00:32:52,900
Let's go in and take a look.

481
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:54,600
I'll go in and take a look.

482
00:33:02,880 --> 00:33:04,080
It's still uncertain

483
00:33:04,440 --> 00:33:07,520
why the suspect deliberately posed the body like this.

484
00:33:27,600 --> 00:33:29,800
Was she strangled with a hemp rope?

485
00:33:36,360 --> 00:33:37,880
The red hemp rope,

486
00:33:39,160 --> 00:33:41,240
the posture of the body,

487
00:33:43,040 --> 00:33:45,200
and the mysterious spell on her back,

488
00:33:46,880 --> 00:33:48,720
they are exactly the same.

489
00:33:49,040 --> 00:33:50,280
Same as what?

490
00:33:54,040 --> 00:33:57,500
Exactly the same as a few unsolved cases from over a decade ago.

491
00:33:58,000 --> 00:33:59,860
The victims were also all female.

492
00:34:00,720 --> 00:34:04,560
The killer tied the victims' bodies

493
00:34:04,600 --> 00:34:06,860
into various shapes with red hemp ropes.

494
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:11,380
But what is the same is that

495
00:34:12,320 --> 00:34:14,239
on every victim's back,

496
00:34:14,360 --> 00:34:19,120
there was a mysterious spell drawn in cinnabar.

497
00:34:23,880 --> 00:34:24,840
Third watch.

498
00:34:24,880 --> 00:34:26,920
All is well.

499
00:34:33,639 --> 00:34:34,400
Whose house is this?

500
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:36,199
The door isn't closed properly.

501
00:34:36,920 --> 00:34:37,850
Is anyone there?

502
00:34:43,960 --> 00:34:45,040
Dead body!

